Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said Koyuki is the best\N我说小雄是最佳人选
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The vocal of your band gotta be Koyuki\N小雄最适合做你乐团的主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He is a genius\N他是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna be a fucking great vocalist\N他会成为一个出色的主唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. We're not target about making a choir hymn\N拜托  我们又不是要组圣歌队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?\N明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not really,you don't understand\N我看是你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在争论什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都听不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得小雄不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐团的主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得小雄能胜任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主唱?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和千叶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum the guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《吉他入门》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《吉他─七星期进阶》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸雄  阿广写信来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了  幸雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在过得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天还在九州钢琴大赛中获得第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白这代表什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这代表下次说不定会到维也纳去比赛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P.S.我已经买到了新出的三国志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前略  阿广
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的来信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我最近开始弹吉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到吉他还是很容易弹的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是范·海伦(Van Helen)啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史蒂夫·派(Steve Perry)啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保罗·吉伯特(Paul GiIbert)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努诺(Nuno Bettencourt)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克·怀德(Zakk Wylde)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野村义男之类的  马上就上手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我正在练的曲子是「四季之歌」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在维也纳一起演奏就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随信附上我在综合体育馆拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东日本吉他大赛中学生级别优胜的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈  我去一下体育馆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要放暑假了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先抓个知了玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对~对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不要理他嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他比我还重要啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和昨天的态度完全不同了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天还对我那么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在老太不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起配合唱来听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙介  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  有什么话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再让我看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再让我看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:10:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先给我游200米热热身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会出人命的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是来渡假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个暑假一定要超越其他学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指导老师是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个临时教练真是严格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每周固定来两次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不算临时的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有人会退出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫他是每周都会游3万米的游泳家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的有44岁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄什么时候加入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在有很大的问题要解决
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能不能顺利解决
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸雄  阿广来信了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你居然开始练吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓了我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的吉他实力应该还远远比不上我的钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道你到了什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次去你那儿玩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹给我听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P.S.维也纳是去不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我去了荷兰村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这不是小雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一次之后都没有在泳池看到你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在弹吉他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦摔坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏了的话  就再也修不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把吉他应该可以修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识一家乐器店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以算便宜点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一个月左右就能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修得好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生可是被英式摇滚改变过的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他它也是  被扔掉是很可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空的话  带上这把吉他来我家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以教教你弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前途茫茫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关小雄的事想问…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把吉他是艾迪送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时对像我这种没有朋友的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一肯伸出友谊之手的就只有艾迪一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是小雄他也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微拿到了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙介  快来帮忙接力拿饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前两天听说了一件怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙介这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没吃过纳豆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间差不多了  该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  演出有什么重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如和我一起制造些浪漫的夏日回忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  两男两女其实正好可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的乐团里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么都要有阿平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有两下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个主唱好烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种主唱也太糟塌阿平了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是以前The Ground的主唱宫泽学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我了  没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认同你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是荣二搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得大家这么支持
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就唱一首玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就唱Music mans也有翻唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heart Breakers的Junny送给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂他唱得有哪里好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F要用食指的侧面来按
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:18:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进步不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音已经弹出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在几个常用的和弦你都记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就用这些和弦连起来弹弹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是手指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就此退缩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可讨不到女孩子喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是为了这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄  看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄  跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我因伤退出奥运会之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我从自暴自弃的深渊里救出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是摇滚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄喜欢哪把呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边那把和龙介用的吉他样子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那把八成是Gibson的Les Pole
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我这把是仿冒Gibson的—Tibson的Les Pole
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前1美金兑360日元的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真货的价格高得让人买不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tibson?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把Les Pole就借给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一个调音器和音箱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,30)}白痴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫贝吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄你听过Rocket Boys这个乐团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时被披头士的光芒淹没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只发行过一张CD就解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个梦幻的英国乐团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我心中的师父
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  在电视里也没见到过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉可是我这个44岁的单身贵族唯一的知己朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他随我弹的曲子唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一直无法达成的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙对于不够水准的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不屑一顾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.78,0:22:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄  要玩就一定要玩到能够让贝吉唱歌的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  既然弹了  就要认真弹好来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好  小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鸟儿不叫  我就让它叫」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,35)}{\fs16}注：后人对丰臣秀吉的为人处事的比喻\N意思就是对于不服从自己的人 就用手段让他服从
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  小雄  要的就是这个志气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,35)}{\fs16}注：后人对织田信长的比喻是「鸟儿不叫 我就杀鸟」\N意思就是对于不服从自己的人 就消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我喜欢的战国武将是信长…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那最后复习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A D G F
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.65,0:24:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚踩两条船被揭穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.37,0:24:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱真是有苦说不出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.87,0:24:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
